For end users:

1. click Code -> Download ZIP file then extract anywhere on your PC/Phone/Tablet

2. dump as many mp4 files you want in /video. filenames should be in this order

video_1
video_2
video_3
video_4
video_5
video_6
video_7
video_8
video_9
video_10

and so on...

4. Launch index.html in your browser

- Default no of videos shown is 16
- Click the lock icon and insert 'durian' as the password to enter your custom no of videos

5. Now your children can enjoy safe "screen time" 

6. More features will be added soon, stay tuned!

